---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Contact Bright Horizon"
  description="Start a conversation with Bright Horizon about IT consulting, security, digital transformation, and growth opportunities across Africa."
>
<section class="soft-gradient border-b border-[#1F7A63]/10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] lg:items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="animate-fade-up text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#175247]">Contact Bright Horizon</p>
        <h1 class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-1 mt-4 max-w-3xl text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#103B34] md:text-6xl">
          Let’s turn your next digital move into a confident business advantage.
        </h1>
        <p class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-2 mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-[#1A1A1A]/80">
          Whether you need IT enablement, cybersecurity support, systems integration, or opportunity facilitation, we structure engagements around practical execution and clear outcomes.
        </p>
        <div class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-3 mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="mailto:info@brighthorizon.co.za" class="btn-primary btn-shine inline-flex rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold">
            Email Our Team
          </a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/27793599604" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#25D366] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-[#25D366]/30 transition hover:bg-[#1FAE53] hover:shadow-[#25D366]/50 active:scale-95">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
            </svg>
            WhatsApp Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section-shell animate-fade-up p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Why Clients Reach Out</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-white/70 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Digital Transformation</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">From ERP and integration to operational modernization and cloud readiness.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-white/70 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Security & Compliance</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Cyber resilience, identity governance, and controls that support growth with confidence.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-white/70 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Market Opportunity</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Regional partnerships and structured opportunity facilitation across key African sectors.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
  <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr]">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="section-shell p-7">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Direct Contact</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/80">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#6A4917]">Email</p>
            <a href="mailto:info@brighthorizon.co.za" class="mt-2 inline-block text-base font-semibold text-[#175247] hover:text-[#103B34]">info@brighthorizon.co.za</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#6A4917]">Mobile</p>
            <a href="tel:+27793599604" class="mt-2 inline-block text-base font-semibold text-[#175247] hover:text-[#103B34]">+27 79 359 9604</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#6A4917]">Landline</p>
            <a href="tel:+278770021060" class="mt-2 inline-block text-base font-semibold text-[#175247] hover:text-[#103B34]">+27 877 002 106</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#6A4917]">WhatsApp</p>
            <a href="https://wa.me/27793599604" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#25D366] px-5 py-2.5 font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#1FAE53]">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section-shell p-7">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Availability</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/80">We engage on a flexible basis, with structured availability aligned to client needs and time zones across Africa and beyond. Priority engagements and cross-border coordination can be arranged by appointment.</p>
        <div class="mt-5 rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-[#FFF9EF] p-5 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/80">
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Response expectation</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Most enquiries receive an initial response within one business day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-shell p-8 md:p-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Start the Conversation</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/78">
        Share your project, security requirement, or partnership brief. We will route your message to the right team and respond through info@brighthorizon.co.za.
      </p>

      <form class="mt-8 space-y-6" action="mailto:info@brighthorizon.co.za" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#103B34] mb-2">Full Name *</label>
            <input
              id="name"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Your full name"
              required
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-[#D8C7A1] bg-white/90 p-3.5 focus:outline-none"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#103B34] mb-2">Company</label>
            <input
              id="company"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Your organization"
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-[#D8C7A1] bg-white/90 p-3.5 focus:outline-none"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#103B34] mb-2">Email Address *</label>
            <input
              id="email"
              type="email"
              placeholder="you@company.com"
              required
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-[#D8C7A1] bg-white/90 p-3.5 focus:outline-none"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#103B34] mb-2">Phone or WhatsApp</label>
            <input
              id="phone"
              type="text"
              placeholder="+27 ..."
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-[#D8C7A1] bg-white/90 p-3.5 focus:outline-none"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="subject" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#103B34] mb-2">Subject</label>
          <input
            id="subject"
            type="text"
            placeholder="What would you like to discuss?"
            class="w-full rounded-xl border border-[#D8C7A1] bg-white/90 p-3.5 focus:outline-none"
          />
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#103B34] mb-2">Message *</label>
          <textarea
            id="message"
            placeholder="Tell us about your goals, your current challenge, and the outcome you want to achieve."
            required
            rows="7"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-[#D8C7A1] bg-white/90 p-3.5 focus:outline-none"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn-primary btn-shine inline-flex rounded-full px-7 py-3 text-sm font-semibold"
          >
            Send to info@brighthorizon.co.za
          </button>
          <a href="https://wa.me/27793599604" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#175247] hover:text-[#103B34]">
            Prefer instant messaging? Start on WhatsApp.
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xs text-[#1A1A1A]/60">
          Your information is used only to assess and respond to your enquiry.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</MainLayout>
